content: God the King of the Earth.
To the Chief Musician. A Psalm of the sons of Korah.
Shout to God with the voice of triumph  songs of joy.
For the  Most High is to be feared [and worshiped with awe-inspired reverence and obedience];
He is a great King over all the earth.
He chooses our inheritance for us,
The glory  excellence of Jacob whom He loves.
